  "description": "Curated, deep starter queries so the first interprocedural taint query needs no agent synthesis. Maintainer-authored; the CodeQL queries use the standard-library security flow modules and the Joern queries follow the KUZUSHI_CPG convention. install-starter-pack copies these into <target>/.kuzushi/rules/ and registers them in the digest-attested pack so the codeql/joern MCP servers will run them. validated.compileVerified is false for shipped queries — they are curated, not machine-compiled at install; run the engine compile check (or CI with the engine present) to verify against a specific CodeQL/Joern version.",
